    "As expected, scenarios were on average more negative (M=3.49, SD = 0.98) than positive (M=1.43, SD=0.86).",
    "We compared both negativity and positivity as rated by participants depending on the scenario in supplementary materials",
    "Comparing the quality of reappraisal between humans and GPT.",
    "We conducted multiple regression to examine whether participants who were assigned to the AI partner condition perceived the received reappraisal as higher quality compared to the human partner condition.",
